re I|Theodore I]]'''\n|Located in the atrium.<ref name=\"rear53\"/> Destroyed during the demolition.<ref name=\"rear53\"/>\n|- valign=\"top\"\n|654\u2013657\n| [[File:PopeeugeneI.jpg|70px]]\n| '''[[Pope Eugene I|Eugene I]]'''<br /><small>Saint Eugene</small>\n|Destroyed during the demolition<ref name=\"rear54\">Reardon, 2004, p. 54.</ref>\n|- valign=\"top\"\n|657\u2013672\n| [[File:Pope Vitalian.jpg|70px]]\n| '''[[Pope Vitalian|Vitalian]]'''<br /><small>Saint Vitalian</small>\n|Destroyed during the demolition<ref name=\"rear54\" />\n|- valign=\"top\"\n|672\u2013676\n| [[File:Adeodatus II.jpg|70px]]\n| '''[[Pope Adeodatus II|Adeodatus II]]''', '''''[[Order of Saint Benedict|O.S.B.]]'''''\n|Destroyed during the demolition<ref name=\"rear54\"/>\n|- valign=\"top\"\n|676\u2013678\n| [[File:Popedonus.jpg|70px]]\n| '''[[Pope Donus|Donus]]'''\n|Destroyed during the demolition<ref name=\"rear54\"/>\n|- valign=\"top\"\n|678\u2013681\n| [[File:Agatho.png|70px]]\n| '''[[Pope Agatho|Agatho]]'''<br /><small>Saint Agatho</small>\n|Destroyed during the demolition<ref name=\"rear54\"/>\n|- valign=\"top\"\n| style=\"background:#c9c0bb;\"|681\u2013683\n| style=\"background:#c9c0bb;\"|[[File:LeoII.jpg|70px]]\n| style=\"background:#c9c0bb;\"| '''[[Pope Leo II|Leo II]]'''<br /><small>Saint Leo</small>\n| style=\"background:#c9c0bb;\"|Originally buried in Old Saint Peter's; translated under the altar of the Chapel of the Madonna della Colonna; combined with Leo I in the early seventeenth century; for centuries believed to be under the altar of the Church of San Stefano in Ferrara; combined remains of Leo's I, II, and IV in Chapel of the Madonna of Partorienti when found during the demolition<ref name=\"rear5455\">Reardon, 2004, pp. 54\u201355.</ref>\n|- valign=\"top\"\n|684\u2013685\n| [[File:BenedictII.jpg|70px]]\n| '''[[Pope Benedict II|Benedict II]]'''<br /><small>Saint Benedict</small>\n|Destroyed during the demolition<ref name=\"rear55\">Reardon, 2004, p. 55.</ref>\n|- valign=\"top\"